short_description: jaaya axel is an educational consultant based in kuala lumpur, malaysia.
long_description: jay excel medic is a public oriented student placement consultant geared towards giving the best services to students commencing from consultation till they graduate. providing detailed information to the public about the courses and universities offering an array of programs. providing free professional consultation to ensure students chose the right course, university and country based on qualification and financial capacity. providing periodic information about students' academic performance. jay excel medic, university & college admission advisory (ja-ucaa) has been engaged in consulting, recruitment and students placement services in the field of education of local and international students in malaysia for the past 12 years. our company gives a chance to undergraduates and graduates, who are passionate about the benefits of study local and abroad, to join the best united kingdom, australia, new zealand, russia, india, indonesia, bangladesh and other universities. our company was registered under malaysian ministry of education in 2001.
